# Kubernetes sample installation

*Note*: This page is not meant to be used as public documentation. It is simply
meant to describe the sample files in this folder.


You must also have a Kubernetes namespace created called "default"

### Setup

As the system:admin user install the following files:

crd.yaml
cluster-role.yaml
cluster-role-binding.yaml
service-account.yaml

To install the operator and the first Couchbase cluster in the default namespace
install the files below to Kubernetes.

operator.yaml
secret.yaml
couchbase-cluster.yaml